From Absor...<br>
<br>
<i><b>"We've also looked a few more rogue issues, and expect to have them adjusted in the following weeks. <u>None of these are promised</u>, keep this in mind, but we are looking into them.</b><br>
<br>
Reduction of Min Range for throwing weapons. Not a removal, but a reduction, to around 3-5 feet. Should make them easier to use. <br>
<br>
Instill Doubt still on the same timer as it is currently, but allowing that first backstab or special attack to land after ID goes off. This will happen. Still rewards those of you with good timing.<br>
<br>
Apply Poison putting the Rogue in kneel mode similar to bind wounds, and releasing him when complete. Great player idea, this will probably happen."</i><br>
